-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT
   TOP 5 tag, COUNT(*) as quantity
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://cp2dl.dfs.core.windows.net/bd-project/Predictions/predictions_2024-05-16_08-08-14.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        PARSER_VERSION = '2.0',
        HEADER_ROW = TRUE
    ) AS [result]

GROUP BY tag
ORDER BY quantity DESC
